This is fix and remake of mg_saw_fix. I added a many of things, who make it more funny and more beautiful.


I added:

- Health charger ahead of freezer.
- HE Grenade for break ice in freezer.
- End room.
- Frag charger in end room.
- Env_cubemaps.
- Many efects (visual and sound).
- 64 Spawn points.
- Command "mp_limitteams 0".

I changed:

- Every light.
- 90% Textures.
- 90% Brushes.
- Many of traps.

I optimized this map.
